name: Tweet and Retweet
description: When I saw all this birds on this antenna I felt lucky to have my telelens with me, I waited for the next bird that was about to land on the antenna and took this picture. It seems like a bunch of tweets and a new Twitter message coming in! Daily photographer, started this account as part of my #TensDaily or #HENten project. Each day a 10/10 free edition, uncollected pieces burned the next day.
